    "name": "Stars of Icarus",
    "steam_appid": 2278950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/a7ae39f73b5df875f7ceb49f81fb7b83.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=233 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《伊卡洛斯之星》是由《Guns of Icarus》背后团队所操刀的最新星舰战斗游戏。在遥远的太空边缘地带，唯一能够依靠的就是团队协作。拉上好友或陌生人组成杂牌小分队，在这款紧张刺激的在线PvP飞船战斗游戏中展开激烈对抗。选择星舰，加入中队，定制配装，成为太空边境令人闻风丧胆的战队。你会坐上星际霸主的王座，还是英勇而壮烈地陨落？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/db41d7e72d6c3ebd3bcddbc1c5bc904a.poster.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/db41d7e72d6c3ebd3bcddbc1c5bc904a.webm?t=1769641242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/56295b0b6064af7cea19aee32373fb81.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/83e3a126ebf2ebe110420fded2454a72.poster.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/83e3a126ebf2ebe110420fded2454a72.webm?t=1769641242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六款星舰和超过25种舰队阵型可供选择，你更愿意在单人战斗机中通过高速袭击实施阵前侦察，还是在双座轻型护卫舰中提供关键火力支援，抑或是在三人巡防舰中操纵重炮狂轰滥炸？不做好充分准备，就准备好失败吧。每场对局开始前，在大厅中决定好中队构成，并定制星舰配装，以便在实战中占据上风。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/fdf22166aeb31ad9271e0bd926d99d11.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/e7622f7d0b1802ae1771d1bd7aa1e02c.poster.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/e7622f7d0b1802ae1771d1bd7aa1e02c.webm?t=1769641242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《伊卡洛斯之星》的灵魂就是团队协作——星舰坠毁，则全员陨落。自定义你的角色，为其装备适当的工具，并组成五人战队，跳入社区服务器中享受传统多人游戏体验！不论你负责的是在宇宙迷雾中掌控航向，还是操纵大炮清剿敌舰，抑或是确保护盾和引擎屹立不倒——团队都离不开你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/0037156f2b0a6440f9919f02837ba69e.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/e0dffb8e2b586d64b75fa2820db835b6.poster.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/e0dffb8e2b586d64b75fa2820db835b6.webm?t=1769641242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建自己的独特角色，装饰星舰，收获冲突战中的奖励。游戏内商店中还有五花八门的装扮选项，但这些物品只会影响外观。《伊卡洛斯之星》拒绝氪金求胜，所有的星舰、工具和武器从一开始就能选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可按照自己的方式享受《伊卡洛斯之星》，不论是勇闯竞技模式，还是在自定义大厅和服务器中与好友共度轻松休闲时光，都会得到我们的全面支持。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/4ec2a1e2b36652360c045455be0ea095.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/997b6e8ec5d184ac3d3237fcfc4e6b34.poster.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/997b6e8ec5d184ac3d3237fcfc4e6b34.webm?t=1769641242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏大厅中讲述你从敌方炮火中死里逃生的经历，炫耀你是如何依靠半个引擎和破损天线在小行星带中闪转腾挪，安然走脱。每个竞技场都会为你与动态环境的交互增添独有的迂回曲折。充分运用自身经验，一着不慎，则功败垂成。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/8e5087dc42f8959482d12c2657917e49.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/1da3847cf87ccdf54576cd3bd99aa306.poster.avif?t=1769641242\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278950/extras/1da3847cf87ccdf54576cd3bd99aa306.webm?t=1769641242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2012年发行的《Guns of Icarus Online》曾是团队合作型PvP星舰体验的先锋之作，而《伊卡洛斯之星》正是这款十多年前旧作的延续，致敬让我们为人所知的游戏和社群。非常激动能为大家带来新的篇章，也期待在浩瀚星海中见到各位。</p>",
